OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FIOPC to investigate water  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpistol police response     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Independent Office for Police      
OL,6, Conduct (IOPC) will launch an          
OL,7, investigation after a 13-year-old boy  
OL,8, was surrounded by armed police when his
OL,9, water pistol was mistaken for a gun.   
OL,11,FThe boy, who is black, was "rammed" off
OL,12,Fhis bike, handcuffed and confronted by 
OL,13,Fmarksmen in Hackney in July.           
OL,15,FThe IOPC initially said the Met should 
OL,16,Finvestigate the complaint, but has now 
OL,17,Fpledged to launch its own inquiry after
OL,18,Fthe boy's mother raised concerns.      
OL,20,FThe Met apologised for "trauma" caused.
